GlassFish - Realms

- Create/configure Realms by going to Configuration > server-config > security > Realms > New Realm

(i) Create adminRealm Realm

Click the New button > New Realm

Name: adminRealm
Class Name: com.sun.enterprise.security.auth.realm.jdbc.JDBCRealm
JAAS Context: jdbcRealm
JNDI: jdbc/admin
User Table: siteuser
User Name Column: username
Password Column: password
Group Table: siteuser
Group Name Column: usergroupid
Digest Algorithm: MD5

Click OK

(ii) Create csRealm Realm

Click the New button > New Realm

Name: csRealm
Class Name: com.sun.enterprise.security.auth.realm.jdbc.JDBCRealm
JAAS Context: jdbcRealm
JNDI: jdbc/cs
User Table: siteuser
User Name Column: username
Password Column: password
Group Table: siteuser
Group Name Column: usergroupid
Digest Algorithm: MD5

Click OK

(iii) Create merchantRealm Realm

Click the New button > New Realm

Name: merchantRealm
Class Name: com.sun.enterprise.security.auth.realm.jdbc.JDBCRealm
JAAS Context: jdbcRealm
JNDI: jdbc/merchant
User Table: siteuser
User Name Column: username
Password Column: password
Group Table: siteuser
Group Name Column: groupid
Digest Algorithm: MD5

Click OK
